trans-unit.source: Creates a service host for a Web-hosted COM+ component.
trans-unit.target: 建立 Web 裝載 COM + 元件的服務主機。

trans-unit.source: This type supports the [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] hosting infrastructure and is not intended to be used directly from your code.
trans-unit.target: 這個型別支援[!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]裝載基礎結構，並不是直接從您的程式碼使用。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.ComIntegration.WasHostedComPlusFactory"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化的新執行個體<xref href="System.ServiceModel.ComIntegration.WasHostedComPlusFactory"></xref>類別。

trans-unit.source: Creates a service host for the specified URI.
trans-unit.target: 建立服務主機為指定的 URI。

trans-unit.source: A string that contains the Web host parameters.
trans-unit.target: 字串，包含 Web 主機參數。

trans-unit.source: An array of URIs for which the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase"></xref> object is to be created.
trans-unit.target: 陣列的 Uri <xref href="System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase"> </xref>是要建立物件。

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase"></xref> object that contains the service host for the specified URI.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase"> </xref>物件，其中包含指定之 URI 的服務主機。
